==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quietness
<hw>Qui"et*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
quiet; freedom from noise, agitation, disturbance, or excitement;
stillness; tranquillity; calmness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I would have peace and <qex>quietness</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quietsome</ent>⟦br⟧
